    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/a1778711116728a2b58d20677e7182bc.poster.avif?t=1771761802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/a1778711116728a2b58d20677e7182bc.webm?t=1771761802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/a1778711116728a2b58d20677e7182bc.mp4?t=1771761802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在一个古老的王国里，在一个古老的国家里，黑暗的邪恶势力苏醒并占领了该国的首都城堡。恶魔和他们的爪牙渗透到王室并窃取了一个古老的护身符，该护身符可以用来提供通往其他世界的通道。如果最古老的恶魔猎手团体没有决定派遣一位年轻但有前途的英雄和他的祖父导师来阻止暗夜恶魔并最终恢复王国的和平，世界实际上就注定要毁灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/474d2b839efd91b0d846efca6fac2cfe.poster.avif?t=1771761802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/474d2b839efd91b0d846efca6fac2cfe.webm?t=1771761802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/474d2b839efd91b0d846efca6fac2cfe.mp4?t=1771761802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会发现与强盗、海盗、僵尸、骷髅和恶魔的动态战斗，有趣和令人兴奋的任务，以及改进你的装备的机会：头盔、盔甲、武器等等。在你的带领下，英雄将经历艰难的命运之路，从一个单纯的乡村男孩成长为一名高贵的铠甲骑士。或者你的监护人可能是一位瞄准良好的弓箭手、一位年轻的巫师或一位美丽的海盗女孩。由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/473d37d12d102b3372659c4b95cb03df.poster.avif?t=1771761802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/473d37d12d102b3372659c4b95cb03df.webm?t=1771761802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/473d37d12d102b3372659c4b95cb03df.mp4?t=1771761802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成所有任务！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集宝藏！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的装备！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败所有老板！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成所有地下城！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/f54e1a801476ec2e3a432679adcff3be.poster.avif?t=1771761802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/f54e1a801476ec2e3a432679adcff3be.webm?t=1771761802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183640/extras/f54e1a801476ec2e3a432679adcff3be.mp4?t=1771761802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
